        <section class="instructions">
            <h3>How to Play</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Click on any column to drop your disc (red)</li>
                <li>Connect 4 discs in a row to win</li>
                <li>Every 5 moves, solve a pattern challenge to continue</li>
                <li>Identify the next item in the sequence</li>
                <li>Get hints if you're stuck on pattern problems</li>
